OL,4,CSchools 'a lifeline to many students'
OL,5,Cin past year'
OL,6, School staff have been giving clothing,
OL,7, food and furnishings to families that
OL,8, have been struggling financially in the
OL,9, coronavirus pandemic, teachers say.
OL,11,FSome pupils have gone to school without
OL,12,Fwinter coats, while others have been
OL,13,Fworried about having enough to eat, a
OL,14,FNational Education Union poll suggests.
OL,16,FThe findings come as the NEU begins its
OL,17,Fannual conference on Wednesday.
OL,19,FThe Department for Education says it
OL,20,Fhas invested #2bn to help pupils in
OL,21,FEngland in the wake of the pandemic.
